<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Green Ops Flier</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@400;600;700&family=Barlow:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/qrcodejs/1.0.0/qrcode.min.js"></script>
<style>
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

html, body {
width: 8.5in;
height: 11in;
background: #0a1a0a;
font-family: ‘Barlow’, sans-serif;
}

.flier {
width: 8.5in;
height: 11in;
background: #0a1a0a;
position: relative;
overflow: hidden;
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
}

.flier::before {
content: ‘’;
position: absolute;
inset: 0;
background: repeating-linear-gradient(
-55deg,
transparent,
transparent 22px,
rgba(60,160,60,0.035) 22px,
rgba(60,160,60,0.035) 24px
);
pointer-events: none;
z-index: 0;
}

.flier > * { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

.top-bar {
height: 10px;
background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1a7a1a, #5ccc3a, #1a7a1a);
flex-shrink: 0;
}

.header {
padding: 0.4in 0.6in 0.18in;
flex-shrink: 0;
}

.badge {
display: inline-block;
background: #1a7a1a;
color: #b8ffb8;
font-family: ‘Barlow Condensed’, sans-serif;
font-size: 9pt;
font-weight: 700;
letter-spacing: 0.22em;
text-transform: uppercase;
padding: 4px 14px 4px 12px;
margin-bottom: 0.13in;
clip-path: polygon(0 0, calc(100% - 10px) 0, 100% 50%, calc(100% - 10px) 100%, 0 100%);
}

.logo-row {
display: flex;
align-items: flex-end;
gap: 0.12in;
}

.leaf-icon {
font-size: 64pt;
line-height: 1;
filter: drop-shadow(0 0 14px rgba(100,220,60,0.55));
}

.brand-name {
font-family: ‘Bebas Neue’, sans-serif;
font-size: 90pt;
line-height: 0.88;
color: #f0fff0;
letter-spacing: 0.02em;
text-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(100,220,60,0.25);
}

.brand-name span { color: #5ccc3a; }

.tagline {
font-family: ‘Barlow Condensed’, sans-serif;
font-size: 13pt;
font-weight: 600;
letter-spacing: 0.2em;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: #7abf7a;
margin-top: 0.08in;
}

.hero-band {
height: 9px;
background: linear-gradient(90deg, #5ccc3a 0%, #1a7a1a 50%, #0a3a0a 100%);
flex-shrink: 0;
}

.intro {
padding: 0.18in 0.6in;
flex-shrink: 0;
border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(92,204,58,0.12);
}

.intro p {
font-family: ‘Barlow Condensed’, sans-serif;
font-size: 13pt;
color: #7aaa7a;
letter-spacing: 0.03em;
line-height: 1.5;
}

.intro p strong {
color: #a8e8a8;
font-weight: 600;
}

.services {
padding: 0.2in 0.6in;
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
gap: 0.15in;
flex-shrink: 0;
}

.service-card {
background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
border: 1px solid rgba(92,204,58,0.18);
padding: 0.17in 0.16in;
position: relative;
}

.service-card::before {
content: ‘’;
position: absolute;
top: 0; left: 0;
width: 4px;
height: 100%;
background: #5ccc3a;
}

.service-icon {
font-size: 20pt;
display: block;
margin-bottom: 5px;
}

.service-title {
font-family: ‘Barlow Condensed’, sans-serif;
font-weight: 700;
font-size: 11.5pt;
letter-spacing: 0.06em;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: #d0ffd0;
margin-bottom: 4px;
}

.service-desc {
font-size: 8.5pt;
color: #5a8a5a;
line-height: 1.55;
}

.why-strip {
margin: 0 0.6in;
padding: 0.16in 0.22in;
background: rgba(92,204,58,0.06);
border: 1px solid rgba(92,204,58,0.2);
display: flex;
justify-content: space-between;
align-items: center;
flex-shrink: 0;
}

.why-item {
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
align-items: center;
gap: 3px;
flex: 1;
}

.why-item + .why-item {
border-left: 1px solid rgba(92,204,58,0.15);
}

.why-num {
font-family: ‘Bebas Neue’, sans-serif;
font-size: 26pt;
color: #5ccc3a;
line-height: 1;
}

.why-label {
font-family: ‘Barlow Condensed’, sans-serif;
font-size: 8pt;
font-weight: 600;
letter-spacing: 0.1em;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: #5a8a5a;
text-align: center;
line-height: 1.3;
}

.spacer { flex: 1; }

.cta-section {
padding: 0.22in 0.6in 0.25in;
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 0.4in;
border-top: 1px solid rgba(92,204,58,0.15);
flex-shrink: 0;
}

.cta-text { flex: 1; }

.cta-headline {
font-family: ‘Bebas Neue’, sans-serif;
font-size: 44pt;
color: #f0fff0;
line-height: 0.92;
margin-bottom: 0.09in;
}

.cta-headline em {
color: #5ccc3a;
font-style: normal;
}

.cta-sub {
font-family: ‘Barlow Condensed’, sans-serif;
font-size: 10pt;
letter-spacing: 0.15em;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: #5a8f5a;
margin-bottom: 0.1in;
}

.cta-url {
font-family: ‘Barlow Condensed’, sans-serif;
font-size: 13pt;
font-weight: 600;
color: #5ccc3a;
letter-spacing: 0.04em;
border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(92,204,58,0.35);
padding-bottom: 2px;
display: inline-block;
}

.qr-wrap {
flex-shrink: 0;
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
align-items: center;
gap: 6px;
}

.qr-box {
background: #fff;
padding: 10px;
width: 1.35in;
height: 1.35in;
display: flex;
align-items: center;
justify-content: center;
box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(92,204,58,0.2);
}

#qrcode canvas, #qrcode img { display: block; }

.qr-label {
font-family: ‘Barlow Condensed’, sans-serif;
font-size: 7.5pt;
font-weight: 600;
letter-spacing: 0.18em;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: #4a7a4a;
text-align: center;
}

.bottom-bar {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
justify-content: center;
background: #5ccc3a;
padding: 0.11in 0.6in;
flex-shrink: 0;
}

.bottom-bar span {
font-family: ‘Barlow Condensed’, sans-serif;
font-weight: 700;
font-size: 10.5pt;
letter-spacing: 0.2em;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: #0a1a0a;
}

@page { size: letter; margin: 0; }
@media print {
html, body { width: 8.5in; height: 11in; }
.flier { width: 8.5in; height: 11in; }
}
</style>

</head>
<body>
<div class="flier">
  <div class="top-bar"></div>

  <div class="header">
    <div class="badge">Professional Lawn Care</div>
    <div class="logo-row">
      <div class="leaf-icon">🌿</div>
      <div class="brand-name">GREEN<br><span>OPS</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tagline">Precision. Pride. Property.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-band"></div>

  <div class="intro">
    <p>Your yard is the first thing people see. <strong>Green Ops delivers reliable, professional lawn care</strong> that keeps your property looking its best — every single week.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="services">
    <div class="service-card">
      <span class="service-icon">✂️</span>
      <div class="service-title">Lawn Mowing</div>
      <div class="service-desc">Consistent weekly or bi-weekly cuts with clean edges and a sharp finish every time.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
      <span class="service-icon">🌱</span>
      <div class="service-title">Fertilizing</div>
      <div class="service-desc">Seasonal treatments that feed your lawn from the roots up for thick, lasting green.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
      <span class="service-icon">🍂</span>
      <div class="service-title">Yard Cleanup</div>
      <div class="service-desc">Leaf removal, debris hauling, and full seasonal cleanups to keep things tidy year-round.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
      <span class="service-icon">🌿</span>
      <div class="service-title">Edging & Trim</div>
      <div class="service-desc">Crisp borders along driveways, walkways, and beds that give your yard a polished look.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
      <span class="service-icon">💧</span>
      <div class="service-title">Weed Control</div>
      <div class="service-desc">Pre- and post-emergent treatments that stop weeds before they take over your lawn.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
      <span class="service-icon">🏡</span>
      <div class="service-title">One-Time Cuts</div>
      <div class="service-desc">No commitment needed. Get a single visit to get your yard back under control fast.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="why-strip">
    <div class="why-item">
      <div class="why-num">100%</div>
      <div class="why-label">Satisfaction<br>Guaranteed</div>
    </div>
    <div class="why-item">
      <div class="why-num">$0</div>
      <div class="why-label">Free<br>Estimates</div>
    </div>
    <div class="why-item">
      <div class="why-num">5★</div>
      <div class="why-label">Rated by<br>Customers</div>
    </div>
    <div class="why-item">
      <div class="why-num">LOCAL</div>
      <div class="why-label">Serving Your<br>Neighborhood</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="spacer"></div>

  <div class="cta-section">
    <div class="cta-text">
      <div class="cta-headline">GET YOUR<br><em>FREE</em> QUOTE<br>TODAY</div>
      <div class="cta-sub">Scan the code · Book online in minutes</div>
      <div class="cta-url">boyerscales.com/greenops</div>
    </div>
    <div class="qr-wrap">
      <div class="qr-box">
        <div id="qrcode"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="qr-label">Scan to book</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bottom-bar">
    <span>🌿 &nbsp; Reliable. Local. Professional. — Green Ops Lawn Care &nbsp; 🌿</span>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
  new QRCode(document.getElementById("qrcode"), {
    text: "https://boyerscales.com/greenops",
    width: 116,
    height: 116,
    colorDark: "#000000",
    colorLight: "#ffffff",
    correctLevel: QRCode.CorrectLevel.H
  });
</script>

</body>
</html>
